{"tid":2284142,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉公子遭票控違限聚令放棄抗辯 怨同行者未有「齊上齊落」","createTime":"2020-11-13T05:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T05:34:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ab1ff1dd3547e3013af6f50627ea5ad8c8cc426","tid":2284142,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:27:29.000Z","msg":"同志富商「劉公子」劉定成今年4月與助手到中環國際金融中心（IFC）商場用膳，遇上市民在商場內進行「和你Sing」行動，最終與途人被警方票控違反限聚令。劉公子原本打算就案件抗辯，惟他日前得悉涉事助手等人已決定繳交罰款，於是在索取證據及法律意見後，決定放棄抗辯，改為繳交罰款了事。惟劉今早到法院欲交罰款時，始知已過了繳款期限，下周仍須出庭應訊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/OVOO6PYAYBB6TBRXBQHC26P5MA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2FOVOO6PYAYBB6TBRXBQHC26P5MA%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIqVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=6cdca685\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2FOVOO6PYAYBB6TBRXBQHC26P5MA%2F&h=77e7cf58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/OVOO6PYAYBB6TBRXBQHC26P5MA/</a>"},{"pid":"2dbc761957686738e943aa689e12208bff0e411e","tid":2284142,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:30:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01b3534396060d286ea04bb39c3682e61fb0f413","tid":2284142,"uid":51469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9ab1ff1dd3547e3013af6f50627ea5ad8c8cc426","tid":2284142,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T05:27:29.000Z","msg":"同志富商「劉公子」劉定成今年4月與助手到中環國際金融中心（IFC）商場用膳，遇上市民在商場內進行「和你Sing」行動，最終與途人被警方票控違反限聚令。劉公子原本打算就案件抗辯，惟他日前得悉涉事助手等人已決定繳交罰款，於是在索取證據及法律意見後，決定放棄抗辯，改為繳交罰款了事。惟劉今早到法院欲交罰款時，始知已過了繳款期限，下周仍須出庭應訊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/OVOO6PYAYBB6TBRXBQHC26P5MA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2FOVOO6PYAYBB6TBRXBQHC26P5MA%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIqVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=6cdca685\" data-ef-url=\"https://em